cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on language modelling using seq2seq models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper introduces a new class of models for sequence learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a method for improving the performance of autoregressive models under small-data conditions. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with neural network models. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper may have applications in image captioning or other tasks that involve sequence learning in computer vision.
